### Create Coupon 1 (Flat Discount)
POST http://localhost:8081/coupons
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "code": "SAVE100",
  "description": "Save 100 on orders above 1000",
  "discountType": "FLAT",
  "discountValue": 100.0,
  "startDate": "2023-01-01T00:00:00",
  "endDate": "2025-12-31T23:59:59",
  "eligibility": {
    "minCartValue": 1000.0
  }
}

### Create Coupon 2 (10% Off Electronics)
POST http://localhost:8081/coupons
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "code": "ELEC10",
  "description": "10% off on Electronics",
  "discountType": "PERCENT",
  "discountValue": 10.0,
  "maxDiscountAmount": 500.0,
  "startDate": "2023-01-01T00:00:00",
  "endDate": "2025-12-31T23:59:59",
  "eligibility": {
    "applicableCategories": ["electronics"]
  }
}

